58#include <openssl/x509.h>
59#include <openssl/x509v3.h>
60
61#include "pcy_int.h"
62
63
64/* accessor functions */
65
66/* X509_POLICY_TREE stuff */
67
68int X509_policy_tree_level_count(const X509_POLICY_TREE *tree)
69 {
70 if (!tree)
71 return 0;
72 return tree->nlevel;
73 }
74
75X509_POLICY_LEVEL *
76 X509_policy_tree_get0_level(const X509_POLICY_TREE *tree, int i)
77 {
78 if (!tree || (i < 0) || (i >= tree->nlevel))
79 return NULL;
80 return tree->levels + i;
81 }
82
83STACK_OF(X509_POLICY_NODE) *
84 X509_policy_tree_get0_policies(const X509_POLICY_TREE *tree)
85 {
86 if (!tree)
87 return NULL;
88 return tree->auth_policies;
89 }
90
91STACK_OF(X509_POLICY_NODE) *
92 X509_policy_tree_get0_user_policies(const X509_POLICY_TREE *tree)
93 {
94 if (!tree)
95 return NULL;
96 if (tree->flags & POLICY_FLAG_ANY_POLICY)
97 return tree->auth_policies;
98 else
99 return tree->user_policies;
100 }
101
102/* X509_POLICY_LEVEL stuff */
103
104int X509_policy_level_node_count(X509_POLICY_LEVEL *level)
105 {
106 int n;
107 if (!level)
108 return 0;
109 if (level->anyPolicy)
110 n = 1;
111 else
112 n = 0;
113 if (level->nodes)
114 n += sk_X509_POLICY_NODE_num(level->nodes);
115 return n;
116 }
117
118X509_POLICY_NODE *X509_policy_level_get0_node(X509_POLICY_LEVEL *level, int i)
119 {
120 if (!level)
121 return NULL;
122 if (level->anyPolicy)
123 {
124 if (i == 0)
125 return level->anyPolicy;
126 i--;
127 }
128 return sk_X509_POLICY_NODE_value(level->nodes, i);
129 }
130
131/* X509_POLICY_NODE stuff */
132
133const ASN1_OBJECT *X509_policy_node_get0_policy(const X509_POLICY_NODE *node)
134 {
135 if (!node)
136 return NULL;
137 return node->data->valid_policy;
138 }
139
140#if 0
141int X509_policy_node_get_critical(const X509_POLICY_NODE *node)
142 {
143 if (node_critical(node))
144 return 1;
145 return 0;
146 }
147#endif
148
149STACK_OF(POLICYQUALINFO) *
150 X509_policy_node_get0_qualifiers(const X509_POLICY_NODE *node)
151 {
152 if (!node)
153 return NULL;
154 return node->data->qualifier_set;
155 }
156
157const X509_POLICY_NODE *
158 X509_policy_node_get0_parent(const X509_POLICY_NODE *node)
159 {
160 if (!node)
161 return NULL;
162 return node->parent;
163 }
